===Noun===
'''[[modal]] [[verb]]'''
#{{grammar}} an [[auxiliary verb]] whose function is to express [[mood]] or [[tense]]
===Usage note===
*In the English language, the modal verbs are - [[can]], [[may]], [[must]], [[ought]], [[shall]], [[should]], [[will]], and [[would]] among others.

